WEBVTT

00:01.400 --> 00:03.868
A peanut butter, banana
and vitamin sandwich?

00:03.936 --> 00:05.303
I'm intrigued.
It's Career
Day at school,

00:05.370 --> 00:06.538
and I have
to figure out

00:06.606 --> 00:08.006
what I'm going to
do with my life,

00:08.074 --> 00:11.409
so, hopefully, a diet
rich in Jif and zinc will help.

00:11.510 --> 00:13.111
Well, if you'd like
to get a head start

00:13.179 --> 00:15.213
I have a witch aptitude test
on my laptop.

00:15.281 --> 00:16.146
Is it accurate?

00:16.181 --> 00:17.148
Are you kidding?

00:17.216 --> 00:19.584
Not only did it
peg me 100%,

00:19.618 --> 00:21.485
but I got into Wellesley.

00:21.520 --> 00:22.286
Okay, I'll try it.

00:22.455 --> 00:23.321
Just put your finger

00:23.422 --> 00:24.489
on the asterisk key,

00:24.523 --> 00:25.990
and it'll show you
your future.

00:26.092 --> 00:27.291
Don't you quit on me.

00:27.359 --> 00:29.928
I need four milligrams
of epi, STAT!

00:29.995 --> 00:31.829
And something for my tummy.

00:34.200 --> 00:36.334
(gurney crashes)

00:36.401 --> 00:37.702
Okay,

00:37.736 --> 00:39.470
either I'm going
to spend my future

00:39.538 --> 00:40.905
being sued
for malpractice

00:40.973 --> 00:42.106
or that test
is wrong.

00:42.174 --> 00:44.275
Salem, did you tamper
with this test?

00:44.343 --> 00:45.410
Took, tampered with--

00:45.478 --> 00:48.346
a cat's got to do
what a cat's got to do.

00:51.217 --> 00:53.685
Tell Elton John
he can start singing now.

00:53.753 --> 00:56.287
(laughs)

